{
  "stem": "21319.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I met him in the first camp, in Vivikond.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was surprised, and I was surprised, because woman were separate and men were separated and children were separate, in separate barracks, you know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and when he saw me, he said, why did you come here?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I came here because otherwise I would have been killed right then in the ghetto, because they liquidated the ghetto and all the people were killed, the rest of them.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, I came because I wanted to save mine child and know that you are here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I haven't-- I-- I saw him, I think, one more time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was no food there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Conditions were horrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There wasn't even water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And every morning, we were taken out to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I-- I remember-- I-- I worked in-- on the railway, which-- a rail fall down on mine leg, broke mine toe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I worked with this potato group, which we went out of-- far away from the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We walked quite far, where they had some potato [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How you say in English.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Buried in-- because of the war, I guess, they were buried in the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we had to dig them out and find the potatoes, because there was no food to bring-- they didn't give us the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They cooked it for the Nazis, for the soldiers, for the guards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So every day, we went potato digging.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But sometimes I-- we used to grab a potato, the Nazi shouldn't see, and eat it, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Raw potato, but something in a history.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Raw potatoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Pieces, what we could, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But there was no food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] There was all this poison water.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
